  <brief_title>A Study of SMT19969 Compared With Vancomycin for the Treatment of Clostridium Difficile-Associated Diarrhoea (CDAD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Randomized, Double-Blind, Active-Controlled Clinical Study to Investigate the Efficacy and Safety of SMT19969 Compared With Vancomycin for the Treatment of Clostridium Difficile-Associated Diarrhoea (CDAD)</official_title>
